author: peter_firmstone
msg: Fix race condition in LeaseExpiration test by making field volatile

Reduce gc thread timing for RegistrarImpl discovery announcement multicast request to two seconds to ensure timed references are cleared before 5 seconds duration, that recommended by the spec, the longer 3.5 second duration was probably resulting in lost announcement requests.
NamedThreadFactory to provide improved debugging output by naming Executor threads.

Added Parallel ClassLoading ability to RFC3986URLClassLoader, only to prevent class loader deadlock that is fixed in Java 7 for clients that need it.  PreferredClassLoader doesn't require parallel class loading so doesn't support it.
